'''苏博科爵士'''（{{lang-fr|Sir Pascal Claude Roland Soriot}}, {{bd|1959年|5月23日||}}）是一位法国企业家。<ref name="Bloomberg">{{cite web|title=Executive Profile: Pascal Soriot|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=11538206&ticker=RO:SW|website=Bloomberg|accessdate=3 April 2015|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924232815/http://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=11538206&ticker=RO:SW|dead-url=no}}</ref>中文名叫'''苏博科'''。

==生平==
1959年出生于[[法国|法国]]，1979年父亲去世，<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/a-drugs-giant-that-loves-to-blind-rivals-with-science-wghxhrpcz|title=A drugs giant that loves to blind rivals with science|last=Ralph|first=Alex|date=17 May 2019|work=The Times|access-date=2019-05-17|language=en|issn=0140-0460|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905035955/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/a-drugs-giant-that-loves-to-blind-rivals-with-science-wghxhrpcz|dead-url=no}}</ref>获得[[巴黎高等商业研究学院|巴黎高等商业研究学院]][[工商管理硕士|工商管理硕士]]学位。<ref name="autogenerated1" />

1986年4月加入[[法国|法国]]第二大制药公司[[罗素-优克福|罗素-优克福]]并担任[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]地区销售代表，<ref name="autogenerated1" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.roche.com/about_roche/management/executive_committee/executive_commitee-pascal-soriot.htm |title=Pascal Soriot |website=Roche.com |accessdate=26 January 2017 |archive-date=2012-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121229085940/http://www.roche.com/about_roche/management/executive_committee/executive_commitee-pascal-soriot.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>1996年升任经理，1997年4月搬迁至[[日本|日本]][[东京都|东京都]]。2000年加入安万特美国，2002年升任[[首席运营官|首席运营官]]，2004年安万特和[[赛诺菲|赛诺菲]]合并后继续留任。2006年加入[[罗氏制药|罗氏制药]]，2009年4月至2010年担任旗下[[基因泰克|基因泰克]][[首席执行官|首席执行官]]，2010年返回[[罗氏制药|罗氏制药]]担任[[首席运营官|首席运营官]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-28/astrazeneca-names-roche-s-pascal-soriot-as-ceo.html|title=AstraZeneca Names Roche's Pascal Soriot as CEO|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=6 February 2013|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006211425/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-28/astrazeneca-names-roche-s-pascal-soriot-as-ceo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年8月被任命为[[阿斯利康|阿斯利康]][[首席执行官|首席执行官]]。<ref>{{cite news |last=Rowley |first=Emma |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/pharmaceuticalsandchemicals/9504462/AstraZeneca-appoints-Roches-Pascal-Soriot-as-new-chief.html |title=AstraZeneca appoints Roche's Pascal Soriot as new chief |work=The Telegraph |date=28 August 2012 |accessdate=26 January 2017 |archive-date=2016-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328071942/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/pharmaceuticalsandchemicals/9504462/AstraZeneca-appoints-Roches-Pascal-Soriot-as-new-chief.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年7月被披露即将担任[[以色列|以色列]]制药公司[[梯瓦|梯瓦]]，随后被否决。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2017/07/14/pascal-soriot-looks-set-stay-astrazeneca-chief/|title=Pascal Soriot looks set to stay as AstraZeneca chief|first=Hannah|last=Boland|newspaper=The Telegraph|date=14 July 2017|via=www.telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=2020-12-13|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031050/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2017/07/14/pascal-soriot-looks-set-stay-astrazeneca-chief/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Reuters Editorial |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-teva-pharm-ind-astrazeneca-ceo-idUSKBN19X2OB?il=0 |title=AstraZeneca's CEO Soriot to join Israeli drugs company Teva: report |publisher=Reuters |date=14 May 2014 |accessdate=12 July 2017 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109034420/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-teva-pharm-ind-astrazeneca-ceo-idUSKBN19X2OB?il=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://endpts.com/israeli-newspaper-reports-that-astrazeneca-ceo-pascal-soriot-has-agreed-to-take-the-helm-at-teva/ |title=Israeli newspaper reports that AstraZeneca CEO Pascal Soriot has agreed to take the helm at Teva – ENDPOINTS NEWS |publisher=Endpts.com |accessdate=12 July 2017 |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008170632/https://endpts.com/israeli-newspaper-reports-that-astrazeneca-ceo-pascal-soriot-has-agreed-to-take-the-helm-at-teva/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年9月公开自己年薪940万英镑，并说“是药企最低薪酬的[[首席执行官|首席执行官]]，在一定程度上造成困扰，但是它就是这么如此。”<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/salary-size-matters-says-astra-zeneca-boss-on-9-4m-vg9c7hm2t|title=Salary size matters, says Astra Zeneca boss on £9.4m|first=Sabah|last=Meddings|via=www.thetimes.co.uk|accessdate=2020-12-13|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127081440/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/salary-size-matters-says-astra-zeneca-boss-on-9-4m-vg9c7hm2t|dead-url=no}}</ref>

